flowRoot.flowPara: The design currently only shows an overview of branches for all apps. - there's no way to show all the branches for one app on its own. This could be added to this page (possibly with a toggle to switch between branch view and store view). However, this risks reproducing a lot of the content from the dashboard.
Other thing to potentially show here: read recent reviews, rating and install breakdowns (by distro, country, language) and trends.
Do we want to show information about apps here? Possibilities: number of builds or branches, number of installs (if that's possible), build frequency, whether they have nightlies available...

These mockups take the approach of having all app and branch settings in one place, and that's the only place you can add new apps or branches. This simplifies how the site is organized and navigated.
